##Business Profit Calculator, which Calculates profit and margin percentage

# User enters revenue and costs
revenue = float(input("Enter total revenue: $"))
costs = float(input("Enter total costs: $"))

# Calculate profit and profit margin
profit = revenue-costs
profit_margin = (profit/revenue)*100

# Display profit and profit margin
print(f"\nProfit: ${profit}")
print(f"Profit margin: {profit_margin:.1f}%")